<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mildew" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mildew,</orth> to taint with mildew, to blight, to blast: <cit><quote>like a --ed ear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 64</bibl></cit> (cf. Genesis XL<bibl n="shak. ham 1.6.64" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 6</bibl>). <cit><quote>--s the white wheat,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 4, 123</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>